<br>
Generally I use 2 steins with a sarnak ceremonial dagger in the range slot, although if not grouped I change the Crude Stein for a Sacrifical Dagger or a Black Tome with Silvery Runes.  The Tome give a bit more mana but the dagger allows you to initiate melee without using mana.  Great for getting a pet started when farming greenies.<br>
<br>
I always aim at maximising both Cha and Int when grouping - so as you have a hope of maintaining enough mana to mez with.  <br>
<br>
Hardy<br>
